  "title": "Beautician",
  "description": "<p><strong>🌸 Hiring: Beautician 🌸</strong></p><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> TGK Beauty (Ang Mo Kio / Bedok North)<br />💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> SGD 4,000 – SGD 5,000 + Attractive Commission</p><p><br />🕒 <strong>Full-Time Position</strong><br /></p><p><strong>About Us:</strong><br />TGK Beauty is a well-established beauty spa offering a range of services, including <strong>facial treatments, waxing, hair spa treatments, and wellness therapies</strong>. We are looking for passionate and skilled <strong>beauticians</strong> to join our team and provide excellent services to our valued clients.<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br />✨ Perform professional <strong>facial treatments, waxing, and hair spa services</strong>.<br />✨ Provide personalized beauty recommendations to clients.<br />✨ Ensure high hygiene and safety standards in all treatments.<br />✨ Recommend and upsell beauty packages based on customer needs.<br />✨ Create a welcoming and relaxing environment for all clients.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />✔ <strong>Minimum 1 years of experience</strong> in facials, waxing, and hair spa treatments.<br />✔ Passionate about beauty, skincare, and customer service.<br />✔ <strong>Proficient in Mandarin</strong> to communicate with Mandarin-speaking clients.<br />✔ Strong interpersonal and communication skills.<br />✔ Positive attitude and a team player.<br /></p><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong><br />🌟 <strong>Competitive salary + high commission + incentives</strong><br />🌟 Professional growth opportunities and career development<br />🌟 Supportive and friendly working environment<br /></p><p>📩 <strong>How to Apply?</strong><br />Interested candidates, please apply directly through MyCareerFuture</p><p>Join <strong>TGK Beauty</strong> and grow your career in the beauty industry! 💖</p>",
